==English==

===Pronunciation===
*[[IPA]]: /ɑɹː(ː)/ <small>[growled “ɹ”]</small> (♪: <sub>╰—</sub> )
{{rfap}}

===Interjection===
'''argh!'''
# ''onomatopoeia'': an utterance expressing dismay, embarassment or frustration.
:* '''''Argh!''' Itʼs already 7:15! Weʼre never gonna make it!''

===Usage note===
''Arrggh!'', ''Aaaarrrggghhh!!!'' or any other variations of the sequence ʻa-r-g-hʼ, all convey the same meaning<!--; all are considered incorrect and/or illiterate nonsense--><!--The post-semicolonic clause is conspicuously POV.—Ed.>.

